cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE

The paper presents a novel automatic approach for OSCC diagnosis using deep learning technologies on CLE images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of CLE images could also relate to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
